{"word":"H3500 - יֶתֶר - Yether - yeh'-ther - Jether","slug":"H3500","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יֶתֶר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Yether"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yeh'-ther"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Jether"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D9;&#x05EA;&#x05E8; - yether</b> - <i>yeh'-ther</i><p/>The same as <a href=\"#/H3499\">H3499</a> <i>Jether</i>, the name of five or six Israelites and of one Midianite: - Jether, Jethro. Compare <a href=\"#/H3503\">H3503</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1956\">H1956</a>, <a href=\"#/H3148\">H3148</a>, <a href=\"#/H3492\">H3492</a>, <a href=\"#/H3498\">H3498</a>, <a href=\"#/H3499\">H3499</a>, <a href=\"#/H3501\">H3501</a>, <a href=\"#/H3502\">H3502</a>, <a href=\"#/H3503\">H3503</a>, <a href=\"#/H3504\">H3504</a>, <a href=\"#/H3505\">H3505</a>, <a href=\"#/H3506\">H3506</a>, <a href=\"#/H3507\">H3507</a>, <a href=\"#/H3508\">H3508</a>, <a href=\"#/H3509\">H3509</a>, <a href=\"#/H4195\">H4195</a>, <a href=\"#/H4340\">H4340</a>"}]}